Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore. we came over to\NMr. Itakura's villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've found out that\Nwe failed to open the e-mail at this villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. answer me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there at the villa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me,\Nwill you, Mr. Itakura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,( 33$)\NContact with the Black Organization\N(Pursuit Edition)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:03:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. answer me!\NI Know you're there at the villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me, Mr. Itakura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we've got no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but to hide ourselves in the blizzard\Nand make it out the back door...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so dark in here that I was having\Ntrouble picking up the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. hey, hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the electrical circuit\Nwent out because of this blizzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't open the mail\Nbecause of this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for trying to receive\Nmail in a mountain villa like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come your answer phone's working\Ndespite the black out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well black outs are frequent in\Nthis area because it snows a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm using a phone\Nequipped with a built-in battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how...\Nyou found out I was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha. ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know all about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you were keeping watch\Nover this villa, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as promised\Nwe're nowhere near you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Ndid you finish the system software?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!\NWhat as that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound of the wind\Ntapping on the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right,\NI SS SNOWING Yeaviy over ere 00...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. I can't use the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this,\Nbut won't you give me the info directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time and place of where\NI should hand this software over to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say it just. once, so listen well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that station that's under\Nconstruction called Kenbashi, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fashionable station that's going\Nto be added to the Toto Subway Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning at midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come and wait in front of coin\NIocker number 0032
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iocated on the basement floor\Nof the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to bring the\Nsystem software, got that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...tomorrow s a bad day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going~to have to be:hospitalized\Nfrom this evening for a health check...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know about it, don't you?\NAbout my bad heart condition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're\Ntrying to buy-time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you still haven't\Ncompleted that software?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... it's completed all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when is it convenient for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I'm discharged from the hospital,\Nso about three to four days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. give me five days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't wait that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Extend your hospitalization!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally got an appointment\Nwith a famous heart surgeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I can't move the date...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were to hand it over to you\Nbefore I enter the hospital,.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the construction people\Nwill be there at daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not convenient for\Nyou guys then, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4:00 then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four hours from now at 4.00 a.m...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring the software to the place *\NI just gave you info on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four hours from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Gunma to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's completed you should be able to\Nbring it with you, shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. ..four hours from now,\NI'll take it there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, don't ambush me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I spot any of your people\Nthis entire deal if off
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you were to force\Nthis software away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,keep in mind that doing so may throw\Nthe method of using this software
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,into the pits of darkness forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sure a cautious fellow,\Njust like rumor has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. four hours from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of locker number 0032\Nat the basement of Kenbashi Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. I got them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. just what do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're going to listen\Nto them and take that software over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not listening-to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lead the conversation so that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the hand over time of the software\Nwould be rushed to 4:00 this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by sounding flustered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The news of Mr. Itakura's death may\Nbe aired when morning comes. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this deal as well as clues about\Nthem will go down the drain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now. the jewelry robber who is at large...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately. it seems that none of the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stations are covering news\Nabout his case yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, this is what you\Nintended to do to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning to tell them to rush\Nthe hand over time to an earlier time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I receive the e-mail from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's erase all traces of\Nus having been here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and get out of here with\Nyour beetle. Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They maybe watching us from\Nsomewhere around this villa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we carelessly go out just like that\Nto the car that's parked outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they may spot us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Vodka or any of his\Npeople were around
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would've easily seen through my lie\Nabout the electrical circuits going out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sO that I cant use the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. that's why you turned\Non the lights to this villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know at the least that\Nnone of his people are at a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where they can see the lights of the villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If"!\NThey probably tracked this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using some alarm system\Nthat would warn them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and specify the computer of the one\Nthey re sending the mail to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case the mail that they sent isn't\Nopened by the receiver of the mail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,part of the members of\Nthe their group will be arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll confirm the contents of this software\Nwith the lap top computer in the beetle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if it's some outrageous\Nsoftware that could
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,be used for a hideous\Ncrime or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to report it to the police
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and specify the place of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they can ambush the culprits\Nand arrest whoever shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to enter a password\Nfor this software too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the e-mail a password's been\Nset between Mr. Itakura and those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, just make a copy of it for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do that either
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's protected with a copy guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under this condition,\Nthe police won't move!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't they always secretly\Narmed with guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you report that there will be\Na deal involving guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,maybe at least two or three\Nofficers will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know how many\Nthose guys have on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. with 2 only a small\Nnumber on our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we're more likely to be\Nbiting off our own heads...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless we find out what their purpose is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and present evidence to the police\Nas to how dangerous they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as how large\Ntheir organization is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have the police come\Nequipped with sufficient men,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'll be difficult to lay our hands on them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...how frustrating...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know that they're coming\Nand yet we can't do a thing about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really. there's still a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a bit dangerous. though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. hey, don't tell me that\Nyou're planning to meet them directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Doc. don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're most probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a flat: after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to call a nearby service station\Nand have them bring us over a spare tire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any service station\Nthat'll come at this time of night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. we may as well relax\Nand wait in the car then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't make it in time for\Nmeeting those guys if we do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that this is God's\Nway of telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to keep from taking dangerous\Naction, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A...car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. well. uh, we got a flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We want to go back to Tokyo.\NBut won't you give us a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoh. what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?\NWe're going in that direction anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gramps,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you familiar with the\Nroads around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. gramps. you get in the front seat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the kid in the back seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to intrude on you\Nwhen you were sleeping. miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I was just kind of dozing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, cool!\NThis is a foreign car, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um. is this car yours. sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've gotten tired of it and was just thinking\Nof getting myself another car though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because this car is really expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he may not look it,\Nhe's the heir to a big company, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sure was close...\NSnowy roads are dangerous after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's not rush and drive safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear something\Nfunny just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stuff that we have in\Nthe trunk probably moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to sweat about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't smoke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget that 1 hate cigarettes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry... that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, to go to Tokyo turn left there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's stopped snowing so I guess\Nwe can get there before 03:00
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why were you guys in Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you skiing with your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds great...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch where you're going!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have driven in\Nthe snow after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something fishy about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do you think\Nyou got honked at already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you that\NI'm not good at driving on snowy roads?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car needs a tune up\Nand hasn't got its safety check yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SO you've got to drive more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to get a safety check\Nfor this car soon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number 2 is written on\Nthe sticker on the windshield!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the inspection'cértificate\Nand depending on the number
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the color of the.sticker'it tells you\Nwhen yousre_supposed to be getting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your next=safety check. rigt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The color is this year's color.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's obvious that you have to get\Nyour safety check by February this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right I remember now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a postcard saying for me to go\Nget my safety check within this month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. sonny. when did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sticker was covered with snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it when the on-coming\Ncar passed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the headlights shined on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the number outside could be\Nseen transparent from the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was "2" because\NI saw it transparent from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it was actually "5"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. t hat's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got a postcard saying that\Nyou had to go get a safety check
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,within the month of February. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you see, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't] just tell you a while ago sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he's a Richie Rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he leaves all the details\Nup to others to do it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He answered you casually\Nbut the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's not even bothered about\Nthe date of the safety check
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you've got to turn right over there,\Nor we won't make it to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean the kid keeps blabbing on so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's such a curious child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. I guess it can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way sonny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About economy picking up and\Nthe new coach of Big Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or about the jewelry robber\Nwho is on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're still so little,\Nyet you like news...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? Was the robber caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still escaping\Nsomewhere in the Gunma area!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. I'm sure they'll be arrested soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to have checkpoints here\Nthere and everywhere like over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,License please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but where did\Nyou come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agh, Officer Yamamura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're, if I remember correctly, Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, Officer Yamamura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this Is a checkpoint to arrest\Nthe jewelry shop robbers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are group of three\Nwearing baseball caps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After robbing a jewelry shop in Gunma
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they abandoned the car they made their
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,getaway with in the\Nmountains and vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one of the three is hurt,\Nso I don't think they got too far away yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ri ht!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we got the report,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be nearby\Ndoing some questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got to the scene of the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to run into the robbers\Nwho fled out of the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I pulled out my gun and said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freeze. freeze. or I'll shoot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the robbers refused to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I fired a warning shot towards them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And. I hit one of the robbers in the tigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-hem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either they had another car stashed\Naway in the mountains before hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or they stole a car that coincidentally\Npassed through and are on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didnst you see some\Nsuspicious looking people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean people who are riding\Nin a car that is not theirs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car tire went flat in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we had them give us a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Agasa. then where is your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called the car dealer and they said\Nthey'd come get it in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I left it in the mountains\Nwith the key inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then. isn't your car in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the robbers got a hold of it\Nand are riding it around
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,maybe you shouldn't-be bothering with\Nus and keeping watch over that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a yellow beetle, so it's easy to spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voices...sound familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I donst think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. may we go now, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh will you take that jacket\Nyou have over your lap. just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See. I haven't been shot or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful, then!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. this is the Agasa residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Gunma Prefectural police?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Dr. Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that the dealers would be\Npicking his car up in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, leaving the car as is in the mountains\Nmay give the robbers a chance to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we have decided\Nto tow it away for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. please tell him to come and\Npick his car up at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. yes. I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're doing in\NGunma at this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he was talked\Ninto by Shinichi again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went sticking their noses\Ninto a criminal case or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see what thrill they\Nfind in looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,faults in others at\Nthe cost of losing sleep .
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see no fun.at all in playing detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spare pair of pursuit glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're going to pick up\Nthe stuff earlier than scheduled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An hour from now. at 4:00
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The place remains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's inn front of the locker in the basement\Nof Kenbashi Subway Station...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Gin about this too. will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get the men ready armed with guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could've gone chicken\Nand called the cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, after the deal,\Nit's good riddance with him anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were planning to get rid of him\Ninside Kenbashi Station to begin with...
